WEBVTT

NOTE Opening text followed by excerpts from 05:48.033–06:22.700 and 07:01.400–07:44.033 of PHA-001.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:12.700
The West did not become less religious. It changed religions. Mental health now supplies invisible causes, authorized interpreters, confession, redemption, ritual language, and moral exclusion. The clinical error beneath it is simple: psychiatry creates a label from symptoms and then says that the label caused the symptoms.

00:00:12.700 --> 00:00:16.000
Nothing can suggest
that this diagnosis is wrong.

00:00:16.167 --> 00:00:21.200
The course arrives with the conclusion
and then makes everything else

00:00:21.267 --> 00:00:22.067
point towards it.

00:00:22.067 --> 00:00:25.067
The person
doesn't meet the criteria for autism.

00:00:25.067 --> 00:00:26.500
Well, they're masking it.

00:00:26.500 --> 00:00:29.567
If the antidepressant didn't work,
then it's autistic burnout.

00:00:29.567 --> 00:00:32.733
And if the patient has a lot of anxiety,
well, that's hidden ADHD.

00:00:32.733 --> 00:00:36.333
This is not competent
diagnosis or clinical reasoning,

00:00:36.600 --> 00:00:40.733
and if nothing can prove your conclusions
wrong, then you are doing theology.

00:00:41.267 --> 00:00:42.267
This is religion.

00:00:42.267 --> 00:00:47.367
And honestly, these courses do feel more
like religious experiences.

00:00:47.367 --> 00:00:48.600
But opening up into what?

00:00:48.600 --> 00:00:52.667
Opening up into a field
where the experts and clinicians

00:00:52.667 --> 00:00:57.200
think that disorders are hiding behind
symptoms like goblins in the attic,

00:00:57.233 --> 00:01:01.867
a field where ADHD and autism become
master keys for depression,

00:01:01.900 --> 00:01:06.667
anxiety symptoms, personality disorders,
and any kind of treatment resistance,

00:01:06.667 --> 00:01:10.900
any kind of medication failure or therapy failure.
This is not mental health care.

00:01:10.900 --> 00:01:12.000
This is brain rot.

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:16.300
You do not need more news articles,
more people,

00:01:16.367 --> 00:01:20.367
more posters
telling men to open up this month.

00:01:20.600 --> 00:01:24.700
We need better clinical reasoning
when they do, and that's why

00:01:24.767 --> 00:01:30.000
mental health is getting stupid
and we need to start pushing back.
